org.usfirst.frc.team2077.video.interfaces

Interface VideoSource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSource, GIFImageSource, GstreamerSource, ImageSource, MappedViewSource, MjpegSource

    public interface VideoSource
    Video input stream.

    Sources are created by Main and are required to have a constructor taking parameter (String name), where name is its configuration property prefix.
